tasks.task_query: Duplicate Background layer as Bg copy
Convert Bg copy to a Smart Object
Apply Gaussian Blur 2 px to Smart Object
Add a Black & White adjustment layer
Unlock background to a layer named Portrait
Add Solid Color fill for the background (#FFD700)
Add a Drop Shadow to the Portrait layer

images.instruction: Click Portrait layer in Layers panel;

tasks.task_query: Place the logo as an embedded object

images.instruction: In Layers panel, click Opacity field;

tasks.task_query: Define a pattern named Demo texture
Create a new layer named Texture
Fill the Texture layer with Demo texture pattern
Add text LAUNCH using the Type tool

images.instruction: Click Horizontal Type Tool in toolbar;
Type LAUNCH in provided tentative text;

tasks.task_query: Center align the text via Paragraph panel

images.instruction: Click the text layer in Layers panel;

tasks.task_query: Apply a red 4 px Stroke to the text layer
